property.name: dialogue
property.value: I'm not sure where you came from but welcome to the overworld. Feel free to meet the locals in our village!

property.name: dialogue
property.value: Welcome to my cabin in the woods. Rabid wolves have disrupted what was once a peaceful area.

property.name: dialogue
property.value: A dark silhouette dropped off a random scroll near the dock last night. Would you mind checking it out?

property.name: dialogue
property.value: Well howdy there, welcome to my cabin! Have you come to help us with the wolf problem? I have a mighty fine reward for anyone who can help.
